summary:
For my PhD at Wageningen University I study the presence of endosymbionts in Dutch greenhouse aphids, and how these endosymbionts affect biocontrol success by altering aphid fitness and resistance to parasitoids.

https://www.wur.nl/en/project/Role-of-endosymbionts-in-biocontrol-of-greenhouse-aphids.htm
